name: Design System - Health Aid Inc.
description:
Some months ago, I released this design system, uncompleted. And I have had little time to revisit it since then. Now I do and I have made some tweaks to some elements and changed the whole thing to depart somewhat from the original.

Definitely still have some work to do, but I'm fairly confident this will help you guys to get started on yours, maybe even use it to build your own. Visit my Dribbble, Behance, Instagram or Facebook page for more updates.


#GoFigma #DesignSystems #HealthDesign
